Desert Stride	KEY:Fighter Dawnflower Dervish ~ Desert Stride		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining_Two														DESC:You can move through 10 feet of difficult terrain each round as if it were normal terrain. This benefit stacks with the benefits provided by the Acrobatic Steps and Nimble Moves feats.																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Rapid Attack	KEY:Fighter Dawnflower Dervish ~ Rapid Attack		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining_Three													DESC:You can combine a full attack with a single move. You must forgo the attack at your highest bonus but may take the remaining attacks at any point during your movement. This movement provokes attacks of opportunity as normal.																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Lightning Strike	KEY:Fighter Dawnflower Dervish ~ Lightning Strike	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining_Four														DESC:As part of a full attack, you can make one additional attack. This attack is at your highest base attack bonus, but each attack in the round (including the extra one) takes a -2 penalty.																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.25

