Buckler Catch	KEY:Fighter Rondelero Duelist ~ Buckler Catch		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining_One														DESC:You can catch you opponent's weapon between your buckler and your forearm, effectively wedging the hafts of polearms and hammers or the flats of blades. This functions as a disarm combat maneuver, and you gain a +4 bonus on the roll. If your attack fails by 10 or more, you suffer a -2 penalty to your AC until the start of your next turn.																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.25
